-attachment-3823284" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3823284" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Bleachers-and-Sabrina-Carpenter.jpg" alt="萨布丽娜·卡彭特 (Sabrina Carpenter) 于 2024 年 12 月 17 日在纽约市举行的第十届年度盟友联盟才艺秀上与 Bleachers 一起表演。 （泰勒·希尔/盖蒂图片社为盟友联盟拍摄）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Bleachers-and-Sabrina-Carpenter.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Bleachers-and-Sabrina-Carpenter-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Bleachers-and-Sabrina-Carpenter-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Bleachers-and-Sabrina-Carpenter-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Bleachers-and-Sabrina-Carpenter-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Bleachers-and-Sabrina-Carpenter-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3823284" class="wp-caption-text">萨布丽娜·卡彭特 (Sabrina Carpenter) 于 2024 年 12 月 17 日在纽约市举行的第十届年度盟友联盟才艺秀上与 Bleachers 一起表演。 （泰勒·希尔/盖蒂图片社为盟友联盟拍摄） </figcaption></figure><figure id="attachment_3823458" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3823458" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3823458" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Sabrina-Carpenter-and-Bleachers-performing-1.jpg" alt="萨布丽娜·卡彭特 (Sabrina Carpenter) 在第十届年度盟友联盟才艺表演中与露天看台一起表演。 （泰勒·希尔/盖蒂图片社为盟友联盟拍摄）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Sabrina-Carpenter-and-Bleachers-performing-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Sabrina-Carpenter-and-Bleachers-performing-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Sabrina-Carpenter-and-Bleachers-performing-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Sabri